                  <paragraph>Bottles of 30 NDC 31722-533-30
       
 
  <br/>Bottles of 60 NDC 31722-533-60
       
 
  <br/>Bottles of 100 NDC 31722-533-01
       
 
  <br/>Bottles of 500 NDC 31722-533-05
       
 
  <br/>Bottles of 1000 NDC 31722-533-10
      

 </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Methocarbamol tablets USP 750 mg are white to off white, capsule shaped, tablets debossed with ‘H’ on one side and ‘115’ on other side .  They are supplied as follows:</paragraph>
